---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import PageHero from '../../../components/PageHero.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="FAQ &amp; Changelog — Tango DJ" description="Frequently asked questions about Tango Toolkit software, licensing, and setup, plus a changelog of recent updates.">
  <PageHero title="FAQ & Changelog" lead="Answers to common questions and a log of recent updates." backHref="/dj/software/" backText="Back to DJ Tools" />

  <section class="faq-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="narrow">

        <!-- Getting Started -->
        <h2 class="faq-category">Getting Started</h2>

        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>What software do I need to get started?</summary>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>You need VirtualDJ 2025 (free) and TigerTango (free). See our <a href="/dj/software/">DJ Tools</a> page for downloads and the <a href="/dj/software-setup/">Software Setup</a> guide for installation.</p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>Do I need to pay for anything?</summary>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>TigerTango and TigerTanda are completely free. Hisstory and TigerTag are $40 each with free trials so you can try before you buy.</p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <!-- Licensing & Purchases -->
        <h2 class="faq-category">Licensing &amp; Purchases</h2>

        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>What kind of license do I get?</summary>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>All purchases are one-time payments with lifetime access. No subscriptions, no recurring charges. Your license works offline and includes all future updates.</p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>How do I activate my license?</summary>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>After purchase, you'll receive a license key by email and on the confirmation page. Open the app, click "Enter Key", paste your key, and click "Activate".</p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>Can I use my license on multiple computers?</summary>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>Your license key can be activated on one machine at a time. Contact us at <a href="mailto:tangotoolkit@gmail.com">tangotoolkit@gmail.com</a> if you need to transfer it.</p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>I lost my license key. How do I recover it?</summary>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>Check your email for the purchase confirmation from Tango Toolkit. If you can't find it, email <a href="mailto:tangotoolkit@gmail.com">tangotoolkit@gmail.com</a> with your purchase email and we'll resend it.</p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <!-- Technical -->
        <h2 class="faq-category">Technical</h2>

        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>Which operating systems are supported?</summary>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>All tools support Windows and macOS.</p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>Is TigerTango compatible with VirtualDJ 2026?</summary>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>We recommend using VirtualDJ 2025. The 2026 release added an audio watermark to the free version. Download VirtualDJ 2025 from our <a href="/dj/software/">DJ Tools</a> page.</p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>How do I report a bug or request a feature?</summary>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>Email us at <a href="mailto:tangotoolkit@gmail.com">tangotoolkit@gmail.com</a> or open an issue on the relevant GitHub repository.</p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <!-- Changelog -->
        <hr />

        <h2 class="changelog-heading">Changelog</h2>
        <p class="changelog-intro">Recent updates to Tango Toolkit software.</p>

        <ul class="changelog-list">
          <li>
            <span class="changelog-date">April 2026</span>
            <span class="changelog-text"><strong>TigerTag v1.0 released</strong> &mdash; Batch metadata tagging for tango music libraries</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="changelog-date">March 2026</span>
            <span class="changelog-text"><strong>Hisstory v1.0 released</strong> &mdash; Real-time spectral gating plugin for hiss removal</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="changelog-date">February 2026</span>
            <span class="changelog-text"><strong>TigerTanda updated</strong> &mdash; Improved track suggestions and Virtual DJ integration</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="changelog-date">January 2026</span>
            <span class="changelog-text"><strong>TigerTango v1.0 released</strong> &mdash; VirtualDJ interface designed for tango DJs</span>
          </li>
        </ul>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .faq-section {
    padding: 3rem 0;
  }

  .narrow {
    max-width: 60rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 1.5rem;
  }

  /* FAQ Category Headings */
  .faq-category {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin: 2.5rem 0 1rem;
    color: var(--color-slate-900);
  }

  .faq-category:first-child {
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  /* FAQ Items (details/summary) */
  .faq-item {
    border: 1px solid var(--color-slate-200);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    overflow: hidden;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .faq-item summary {
    padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
    cursor: pointer;
    background: white;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--color-slate-800);
    list-style: none;
    transition: background 0.15s;
  }

  .faq-item summary::-webkit-details-marker {
    display: none;
  }

  .faq-item summary::before {
    content: "\25B8 ";
    color: var(--color-slate-400);
    margin-right: 0.35rem;
  }

  .faq-item[open] summary::before {
    content: "\25BE ";
  }

  .faq-item summary:hover {
    background: var(--color-slate-50);
  }

  .faq-answer {
    padding: 0 1.5rem 1.25rem;
  }

  .faq-answer p {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--color-slate-600);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .faq-answer a {
    color: var(--color-primary);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .faq-answer a:hover {
    color: var(--color-primary-hover);
  }

  /* Changelog */
  .changelog-heading {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
  }

  .changelog-intro {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-slate-600);
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem;
  }

  .changelog-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .changelog-list li {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    padding: 1rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-slate-200);
    align-items: baseline;
  }

  .changelog-list li:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .changelog-date {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-orange-600);
    min-width: 7rem;
  }

  .changelog-text {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--color-slate-700);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .changelog-text strong {
    color: var(--color-slate-900);
  }

  /* Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .changelog-list li {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.25rem;
    }
  }
</style>
